    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 0.8
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 0.8
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 0.7
ELSEIF ABL:새드끼 == 2
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.0
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.0
