ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:마조끼 == 3
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.3
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.1
ELSEIF ABL:PLAYER:마조끼 == 4
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.8
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.2
ELSE
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 2.0
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.8
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.5
ENDIF

;조교자가 왕M
IF TALENT:PLAYER:초M
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.5
