ENDIF
;왕S
IF TALENT:초S
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.5
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.5
    TIMES DOWNBASE:PLAYER:체력 , 1.5
