;새드
ELSEIF TALENT:81
    TIMES SOURCE:14 , 1.2
    TIMES SOURCE:16 , 1.2
    TIMES SOURCE:17 , 1.2
    TIMES DOWNBASE:PLAYER:체력 , 1.2
    TIMES DOWNBASE:PLAYER:기력 , 1.2
ENDIF

